        "comment": {
          "commentType": "FUNCTION",
          "texts": [
            {
              "value": "Plays an essential role in cytoplasmic secondary envelopment during viral egress. Interacts with the capsid via the large tegument protein/LTP and participates in its transport to the host trans-Golgi network (TGN) where secondary envelopment occurs. Modulates tegumentation and capsid accumulation at the viral assembly complex"
            }
          ]
